In re DRESSER et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 25, 1906.) No. 281. Petition to Review Order ol‘ the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. J. A. Hodge, for petitioner.

Before WALLACE. TOWNSEND, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (144 Fed. 318) affirmed in open court.
